~ start
Olivia: [[Hey|Hiya|Hey there]], I'm Olivia the one in charge of running this shop stall
Olivia: Tell me what brings you to my humble shop?
- I want to buy some stuff
	Olivia: What do you want to buy?
	- Corn seeds
		set item_name = "corn seed"
		set item_price = 10
	- Tomato seed
		set item_name = "tomato seed"
		set item_price = 15
	if CoinsManager.coins >= item_price
		Olivia: Here you are. Take this {{item_name}}
		do CoinsManager.remove_coins(item_price)
		do InventoryManager.add_collectable(item_name)
	else
		Olivia: You don't have enough money. {{item_name}} costs {{item_price}} coins

- I want to sell some of my farm products
	Olivia: Which products do you want to sell?
	- Log
		set item_name = "log"
		set item_price = 5
	- Stone
		set item_name = "stone"
		set item_price = 10
	- Corn
		set item_name = "corn"
		set item_price = 20
	- Tomato
		set item_name = "tomato"
		set item_price = 30
	- Egg
		set item_name = "egg"
		set item_price = 40
	- Milk
		set item_name = "milk"
		set item_price = 50
	if InventoryManager.inventory.has(item_name)
		if InventoryManager.inventory[item_name] > 0
			Olivia: Take these {{item_price}} coins
			do CoinsManager.add_coins(item_price)
			do InventoryManager.remove_collectable(item_name)
			=> END
	Olivia: You don't have this item
- Never mind
=> END